spec_data.Name: rkhunter
spec_data.Description:
Rootkit Hunter (RKH) is an easy-to-use tool which checks
computers running UNIX (clones) for the presence of rootkits
and other unwanted tools.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 12 Aug 2017 03:24:28 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A host-based tool to scan for rootkits, backdoors and local exploits
